<br>
Mages are your friend.<br>
<br>
You keep talking about being out of breath too quickly.. As a mage, when I set my mind to making shit dead when we have too many in the camp it dies fast, even with my sub-wizard nukes.  If I could drop every mob that group pulled that fast, it would be sick.  Also, when the acrylia nerf came, many wizards said they could solo for exp almost as good, and acrylia was just a more fun way of doing it.  Either solo or go do AE groups, if you feel out of place in a traditional exp group, don't join them.<br>
<br>
If you're running out of breath too quickly on big fights, take a step back and rethink your strategy.  Mana should almost never be a problem on boss fights.<br>
